data.description: Fantastic income producing Multifamily in the heart of Miami Beach. Solid rent income. P&L upon request. Located  on the desirable North Beach. Just minutes away from restaurants, stores, public transportation, supermarkets,  Collins Ave and trendy South Beach. The land goes from Marseille Dr all the way to Calais Dr, with parking on and  access from both streets. The property consists of 4 - 2 bedroom 1 bathroom units. Community laundry operated  with coins, fenced, licenses up to date and new 40 year cert. Units updated. Financials in the attachments section.
